The crossing of the paths we have

29
00:01:35,690 --> 00:01:39,860
walked upon was by divine design

30
00:01:40,650 --> 00:01:41,780
Inner-soul decisions

31
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:44,990
obstructed by a block of ice

32
00:01:44,990 --> 00:01:48,080
Through spending time together

33
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,660
with you

34
00:01:49,660 --> 00:01:52,620
melted with your single touch

35
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:55,580
The sound of one becomes a two

36
00:01:55,580 --> 00:01:59,460
